  "mainHtml": "<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<nav class=\"flex text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">\n<ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]\">chevron_right</span></li>\n<li class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Supply Management</li>\n</ol>\n</nav>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row xl:items-end xl:justify-between gap-4\">\n<div>\n<h1 class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface m-0\">Supply Management</h1>\n<p class=\"text-body-md font-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">Manage outsourced orders, supplier deliveries, scan-based progress uploads, and exception coordination from one supply-fulfillment command page.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n<button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">add_task</span>Create Outsourcing Task</button>\n<button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">download</span>Export Delivery Report</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">inventory_2</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary bg-primary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">12 Added Today</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Outsourcing Order Pool</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">186</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">Covers machining, sheet metal, heat treatment, and finishing collaboration orders.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">local_shipping</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-secondary bg-secondary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">74 In Transit</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Deliveries in Execution</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">92</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">Active supplier work orders, shipment nodes, and inbound receiving are summarized live.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">qr_code_scanner</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary bg-primary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">92% Return Rate</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Scan Progress Uploads</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">418</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">Start, first article, patrol check, completion, and shipment nodes have been scanned back.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">warning</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-error-container bg-error-container px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">11 Need Action</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">Delay &amp; Exception Alerts</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">11</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">Lead-time drift, quality issues, shortages, and unscanned nodes are aggregated here.</p></div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-5\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">Outsourcing Collaboration Board</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">Manage outsourcing release, production execution, shipping, and receiving confirmation by current order stage.</p></div><button class=\"px-3 h-9 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest text-body-md text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\">Adjust Priority</button></div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\">\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">Pending Outsourcing Release</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-label-sm\">28</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>Housing 5-axis finishing</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">8 Orders</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>Sheet metal bending &amp; welding</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">11 Orders</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>Anodizing &amp; sandblasting</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">9 Orders</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">In Production</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-label-sm\">92</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\"><span>Batch CNC machining</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">63%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[63%] bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\"><span>Finishing schedule</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">48%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[48%] bg-secondary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\"><span>Assembly &amp; final inspection</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">35%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[35%] bg-tertiary rounded-full\"></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">Pending Shipment / Receiving</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-label-sm\">26</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>Waiting for supplier shipment</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">17</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>Waiting for warehouse receipt</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">6</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>Waiting for IQC inspection</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">3</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">Supply Collaboration Suggestions</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-label-sm\">AI Suggestion</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\"><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>Merge anodizing orders into one supplier batch to reduce logistics turnaround cost.</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>Trigger automated reminders for 5 suppliers that still have not scanned first article or patrol checkpoints.</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>Delay-risk orders should trigger joint collaboration between service and purchasing in advance.</span></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-5 space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">Exceptions &amp; Pending Actions</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">Handle delays, shortages, quality issues, and missing scan uploads in one place.</p></div><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-label-sm font-label-sm\">Priority Sorted</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">Spindle Seat Batch Parts</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">2 Days Late</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">Supplier: Kunshan Precision · Cause: heat-treatment schedule congestion</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-body-md\">Delay Request</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">Customer Sync Needed</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">Robot Bracket Assembly</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">Patrol Scan Missing</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">Supplier: Ningbo 5-Axis Center · Production started but patrol checkpoint has not been uploaded.</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-body-md\">Push Scan Reminder</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">Auto Reminder Sent</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">Aluminum Housing</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">IQC Awaiting Decision</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">Warehouse already received the batch, but QC report and batch tags do not match.</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-body-md\">Quality Exception</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">Supplier Evidence Pending</span></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">Scan Upload Mechanism</h3><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">Supplier Fulfillment Standard</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">qr_code_scanner</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Production Milestone Scanning</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Start, first article, patrol check, completion, and shipment must all be scanned back.</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">photo_camera</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Photos &amp; Attachments as Evidence</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">Critical nodes require on-site photos, inspection reports, or logistics documents.</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">notifications_active</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">Automatic Overdue Reminders</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">A node that is missing for 4 hours triggers reminders, and after 12 hours it escalates to operations.</div></div></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div><section class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden mb-8\"><div class=\"p-4 border-b border-outline-variant/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-3 bg-surface-bright\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">This Week's Delivery Overview</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">Review key outsourced orders, current scan milestones, ETA, and exception status at a glance.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><button class=\"p-2 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container rounded transition-colors border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">filter_list</span></button><button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">route</span>View All Collaborative Orders</button></div></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto w-full\"><table class=\"w-full text-left border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-surface-container-low border-b border-outline-variant/50\"><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">Order / Operation</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">Supplier</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">Current Node</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">Scan Upload</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider text-right\">ETA</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider text-center\">Status</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest\"><tr class=\"hover:bg-surface-container/50 transition-colors\"><td class=\"px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">PO-240701 / Spindle Seat 5-Axis Finish</div><div class=\"text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant text-[11px]\">Source: platform order SO-88104</div></td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Kunshan Precision</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">First Article Inspection</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">First article photos + inspection sheet uploaded</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-right text-mono-data text-on-surface\">07-08 16:00</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-[11px] font-medium\">Normal</span></td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-surface-container/50 transition-colors\"><td class=\"px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">PO-240688 / Aluminum Housing Anodizing</div><div class=\"text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant text-[11px]\">Source: awarded RFQ batch RFQ-3226</div></td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Suzhou Finishing Center</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Finishing Schedule</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Patrol checkpoint upload pending</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-right text-mono-data text-on-surface\">07-07 19:30</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-[11px] font-medium\">Alert</span></td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-surface-container/50 transition-colors\"><td class=\"px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">PO-240672 / Robot Bracket Welded Assembly</div><div class=\"text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant text-[11px]\">Source: MES outsourcing rework order WO-5412</div></td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Ningbo 5-Axis Center</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Production in Progress</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">Started, but patrol checkpoint not scanned</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-right text-mono-data text-on-surface\">07-09 12:00</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-[11px] font-medium\">Follow Up</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></section>"
}
